title: Bobby Helps Listener Struggling With Online Dating + Raymundo's Dumb COVID Move + Lunchbox vs. Electric Company!
itunes:title: Bobby Helps Listener Struggling With Online Dating + Raymundo's Dumb COVID Move + Lunchbox vs. Electric Company!
description:
A listener calls in with an issue he's having with online dating and women not looking like their profile pictures. Raymundo didn’t realize something about getting his vaccine and did something dumb. Plus, Lunchbox thinks the electric company owes him money after going without power over the weekend and having to throw out food!
